FFmpeg licensing notice
=======================

This extension supports using an external FFmpeg binary by default, and may
optionally use a packaged FFmpeg binary in custom distributions.

FFmpeg is licensed under GNU LGPL v2.1+ or GNU GPL v2+ depending on how the
binary is built and which optional codecs/libraries are enabled.

When distributing embedded binaries, include:
- The exact FFmpeg build information and configuration flags.
- The applicable LGPL/GPL license text.
- Any third-party codec/library license notices required by that build.

Official project and licensing details:
https://ffmpeg.org/legal.html
